@page "/"
@layout MarketingLayout

<PageTitle>NavTour - Upload Screenshots. AI Builds Your Tour.</PageTitle>
<HeadContent>
    <meta name="description" content="Upload screenshots and AI generates a complete interactive product tour in 60 seconds. AI-powered voiceover, smart annotations, and lead capture built in." />
    <meta property="og:title" content="NavTour - Upload Screenshots. AI Builds Your Tour." />
    <meta property="og:description" content="The AI demo platform that turns screenshots into interactive product tours in under 60 seconds." />
    <meta property="og:url" content="https://navtour.cloud/" />
    <meta property="og:image" content="https://navtour.cloud/images/product-form-builder.png" />
    <meta name="twitter:card" content="summary_large_image" />
    <meta property="og:type" content="website" />
    <meta property="og:site_name" content="NavTour" />
    <link rel="canonical" href="https://navtour.cloud/" />
    <link rel="alternate" hreflang="en" href="https://navtour.cloud/" />
    <link rel="alternate" hreflang="es" href="https://navtour.cloud/?culture=es&amp;ui-culture=es" />
    <link rel="alternate" hreflang="x-default" href="https://navtour.cloud/" />
</HeadContent>

<HeroSection
    Eyebrow="Self-Serve Interactive Demos"
    Title="Upload Screenshots. AI Builds Your Tour."
    Subtitle="Capture your product, generate a polished interactive tour in under 60 seconds, and publish without waiting on a sales call. Built for teams that want to try, launch, and iterate on their own."
    PrimaryCtaText="Start Free ->"
    PrimaryCtaUrl="/register"
    SecondaryCtaText="Explore Product"
    SecondaryCtaUrl="/product"
    ImageUrl="/images/product-form-builder.png">
    <div class="mkt-hero-proof">
        <div class="mkt-hero-proof-item">No credit card required</div>
        <div class="mkt-hero-proof-item">Publish your first tour today</div>
        <div class="mkt-hero-proof-item">Built-in lead capture and analytics</div>
    </div>
    <div class="mkt-hero-mini-metrics">
        <div class="mkt-hero-mini-metric">
            <strong>60s</strong>
            <span>AI-generated first draft</span>
        </div>
        <div class="mkt-hero-mini-metric">
            <strong>24+</strong>
            <span>voices ready to preview</span>
        </div>
        <div class="mkt-hero-mini-metric">
            <strong>HTML/CSS</strong>
            <span>captured with visual fidelity</span>
        </div>
    </div>
</HeroSection>

<section class="mkt-social-proof">
    <div class="mkt-container">
        <div class="mkt-self-serve-strip reveal">
            <div class="mkt-self-serve-strip-copy">
                <div class="mkt-eyebrow">Built for self-serve evaluation</div>
                <h2>Try the product before you talk to anyone.</h2>
                <p>NavTour is positioned for teams that want immediate access: sign up, capture screens, generate a tour, and decide later whether you need a full demo or a paid plan.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="mkt-self-serve-strip-grid">
                <div class="mkt-self-serve-tile">
                    <strong>Start free</strong>
                    <span>Create an account and build without a credit card.</span>
                </div>
                <div class="mkt-self-serve-tile">
                    <strong>Ship fast</strong>
                    <span>Publish a usable walkthrough the same day you sign up.</span>
                </div>
                <div class="mkt-self-serve-tile">
                    <strong>Prove value</strong>
                    <span>See leads, completion, and share behavior from the first demo.</span>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</section>

<section class="mkt-section">
    <div class="mkt-container">
        <div class="mkt-section-heading reveal">
            <div class="mkt-eyebrow" style="color:var(--nt-accent)">Powered by Claude AI</div>
            <h2>One Click. Complete Tour.</h2>
            <p style="max-width:600px;margin:var(--space-4) auto 0;color:var(--text-secondary);font-size:var(--text-lg)">
                Click "AI Generate" in the editor and Claude analyzes every frame of your demo, identifying UI elements, generating step-by-step annotations, and writing voiceover scripts.
            </p>
        </div>

        <div class="mkt-grid mkt-grid-3 reveal-stagger" style="margin-top:var(--space-12)">
            <div class="mkt-feature-card mkt-card">
                <div class="mkt-feature-icon">
                    <svg width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="var(--nt-accent)" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round"><rect x="3" y="3" width="18" height="18" rx="2"/><circle cx="8.5" cy="8.5" r="1.5"/><path d="m21 15-3.086-3.086a2 2 0 0 0-2.828 0L6 21"/></svg>
                </div>
                <h3>Screenshot Analysis</h3>
                <p>AI reads your HTML frames and understands the UI layout, navigation patterns, and key elements without manual tagging.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="mkt-feature-card mkt-card">
                <div class="mkt-feature-icon">
                    <svg width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="var(--nt-accent)" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round"><path d="M21 15a2 2 0 0 1-2 2H7l-4 4V5a2 2 0 0 1 2-2h14a2 2 0 0 1 2 2z"/></svg>
                </div>
                <h3>Smart Annotations</h3>
                <p>Generate titled tooltips with contextual descriptions and sensible positioning for every screen in the flow.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="mkt-feature-card mkt-card">
                <div class="mkt-feature-icon">
                    <svg width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="var(--nt-accent)" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round"><path d="M12 1a3 3 0 0 0-3 3v8a3 3 0 0 0 6 0V4a3 3 0 0 0-3-3z"/><path d="M19 10v2a7 7 0 0 1-14 0v-2"/><line x1="12" y1="19" x2="12" y2="23"/></svg>
                </div>
                <h3>Voiceover Scripts</h3>
                <p>Natural, conversational voiceover text for every step, ready for AI voice generation with 24+ ElevenLabs voices.</p>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</section>

<section class="mkt-section-alt">
    <div class="mkt-container">
        <div class="mkt-step-row reveal">
            <div class="mkt-step-row-content">
                <div class="mkt-eyebrow" style="color:var(--nt-accent)">AI Voiceover</div>
                <h3>Your Demos Speak - In Any Language</h3>
                <p>Choose from 24+ natural AI voices powered by ElevenLabs. English, Spanish, and more. The multilingual model auto-detects your text language and speaks with the right accent.</p>
                <ul style="list-style:none;padding:0;margin:var(--space-6) 0 0;display:flex;flex-direction:column;gap:var(--space-3)">
                    <li style="display:flex;align-items:center;gap:var(--space-3);color:var(--text-secondary);font-size:var(--text-sm)">
                        <svg width="16" height="16" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="var(--nt-accent)" stroke="none"><path d="M9 16.17L4.83 12l-1.42 1.41L9 19 21 7l-1.41-1.41z"/></svg>
                        24+ natural AI voices
                    </li>
                    <li style="display:flex;align-items:center;gap:var(--space-3);color:var(--text-secondary);font-size:var(--text-sm)">
                        <svg width="16" height="16" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="var(--nt-accent)" stroke="none"><path d="M9 16.17L4.83 12l-1.42 1.41L9 19 21 7l-1.41-1.41z"/></svg>
                        Multilingual output with auto-detected language
                    </li>
                    <li style="display:flex;align-items:center;gap:var(--space-3);color:var(--text-secondary);font-size:var(--text-sm)">
                        <svg width="16" height="16" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="var(--nt-accent)" stroke="none"><path d="M9 16.17L4.83 12l-1.42 1.41L9 19 21 7l-1.41-1.41z"/></svg>
                        Instant preview before publishing
                    </li>
                    <li style="display:flex;align-items:center;gap:var(--space-3);color:var(--text-secondary);font-size:var(--text-sm)">
                        <svg width="16" height="16" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="var(--nt-accent)" stroke="none"><path d="M9 16.17L4.83 12l-1.42 1.41L9 19 21 7l-1.41-1.41z"/></svg>
                        Generated once and reused on every play
                    </li>
                </ul>
            </div>
            <div class="mkt-step-row-visual">
                <div class="mkt-stage-card">
                    <div class="mkt-stage-card-header">
                        <div>
                            <div class="mkt-stage-card-label">Voice Preview</div>
                            <div class="mkt-stage-card-title">Multilingual narration</div>
                        </div>
                        <div class="mkt-stage-pill">Ready to publish</div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="mkt-voice-list">
                        <div class="mkt-voice-row"><span>Rachel</span><span>English</span></div>
                        <div class="mkt-voice-row"><span>George</span><span>British</span></div>
                        <div class="mkt-voice-row"><span>Charlie</span><span>Spanish</span></div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="mkt-waveform" aria-hidden="true">
                        <span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</section>

<section class="mkt-section">
    <div class="mkt-container">
        <div class="mkt-section-heading reveal">
            <h2>Three Steps to a Live Demo</h2>
        </div>
        <div class="reveal-stagger" style="display:flex;flex-direction:column;gap:var(--space-16)">
            <div class="mkt-step-row">
                <div class="mkt-step-row-content">
                    <div class="mkt-step-label">Step 1</div>
                    <h3>Capture Your Product</h3>
                    <p>Install the NavTour Chrome extension and browse your product. Click to capture each screen. The extension snapshots the full HTML and CSS, preserving every detail.</p>
                </div>
                <div class="mkt-step-row-visual">
                    <div class="mkt-stage-card">
                        <div class="mkt-stage-card-header">
                            <div>
                                <div class="mkt-stage-card-label">Browser Capture</div>
                                <div class="mkt-stage-card-title">Live extension session</div>
                            </div>
                            <div class="mkt-stage-pill">Recording</div>
                        </div>
                        <div class="mkt-browser-bar">
                            <span></span><span></span><span></span>
                        </div>
                        <div class="mkt-ui-block mkt-ui-block-lg"></div>
                        <div class="mkt-ui-grid">
                            <div class="mkt-ui-block"></div>
                            <div class="mkt-ui-block"></div>
                            <div class="mkt-ui-block"></div>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="mkt-step-row">
                <div class="mkt-step-row-content">
                    <div class="mkt-step-label">Step 2</div>
                    <h3>AI Generates Your Tour</h3>
                    <p>Click "AI Generate" and Claude analyzes every frame. In under 60 seconds, you have a complete interactive tour with step-by-step annotations and voiceover scripts.</p>
                </div>
                <div class="mkt-step-row-visual">
                    <div class="mkt-stage-card">
                        <div class="mkt-stage-card-header">
                            <div>
                                <div class="mkt-stage-card-label">AI Generate</div>
                                <div class="mkt-stage-card-title">Tour draft in progress</div>
                            </div>
                            <div class="mkt-stage-pill">~60s</div>
                        </div>
                        <div class="mkt-progress-stack">
                            <div class="mkt-progress-row"><span>Analyzing frames</span><div><i style="width:92%"></i></div></div>
                            <div class="mkt-progress-row"><span>Placing annotations</span><div><i style="width:78%"></i></div></div>
                            <div class="mkt-progress-row"><span>Writing voiceover</span><div><i style="width:64%"></i></div></div>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="mkt-step-row">
                <div class="mkt-step-row-content">
                    <div class="mkt-step-label">Step 3</div>
                    <h3>Share and Capture Leads</h3>
                    <p>Publish your demo with one click. Share via link, embed on your website, or send via email. Built-in analytics track engagement and the lead capture form converts viewers into pipeline.</p>
                </div>
                <div class="mkt-step-row-visual">
                    <div class="mkt-stage-card">
                        <div class="mkt-stage-card-header">
                            <div>
                                <div class="mkt-stage-card-label">Share Results</div>
                                <div class="mkt-stage-card-title">Leads and engagement</div>
                            </div>
                            <div class="mkt-stage-pill">Live</div>
                        </div>
                        <div class="mkt-result-grid">
                            <div><strong>128</strong><span>views</span></div>
                            <div><strong>47%</strong><span>completion</span></div>
                            <div><strong>19</strong><span>leads</span></div>
                            <div><strong>8</strong><span>shares</span></div>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</section>

<section class="mkt-section-alt">
    <div class="mkt-container">
        <div class="mkt-section-heading reveal">
            <h2>Built for Every Team in the Buyer Journey</h2>
        </div>
        <div class="mkt-grid mkt-grid-3 reveal-stagger">
            <BuyerJourneyCard Icon="website" Title="Website Visitors" Description="Embed interactive demos on your website so prospects can explore your product before booking a call." />
            <BuyerJourneyCard Icon="discovery" Title="Sales Discovery" Description="Send personalized demos before meetings so prospects arrive educated and ready to buy." />
            <BuyerJourneyCard Icon="email" Title="Email Campaigns" Description="Include demo links in outbound sequences to increase reply rates and shorten sales cycles." />
            <BuyerJourneyCard Icon="champion" Title="Champion Enablement" Description="Arm internal champions with shareable demos they can forward to decision makers." />
            <BuyerJourneyCard Icon="tradeshow" Title="Events and Tradeshows" Description="Run demos on booth displays or share QR codes that link to self-guided product tours." />
            <BuyerJourneyCard Icon="onboarding" Title="Customer Onboarding" Description="Guide new users through your product with interactive walkthroughs that reduce time-to-value." />
        </div>
    </div>
</section>

<section class="mkt-section">
    <div class="mkt-container">
        <div class="mkt-section-heading reveal">
            <h2>Everything You Need to Demo Your Product</h2>
        </div>
        <div class="mkt-grid mkt-grid-3 reveal-stagger" style="margin-top:var(--space-8)">
            <FeatureCard Icon="auto_awesome" Title="AI Tour Generator" Description="Claude AI analyzes your screens and generates complete tours with annotations and voiceover in 60 seconds." />
            <FeatureCard Icon="mic" Title="AI Voiceover" Description="24+ natural ElevenLabs voices. Multilingual. Preview instantly. Audio cached with no per-play costs." />
            <FeatureCard Icon="web" Title="Chrome Capture" Description="Snapshot any web app with pixel-perfect HTML/CSS preservation. Computed styles ensure SPA support." />
            <FeatureCard Icon="edit" Title="Visual Editor" Description="Drag annotations, resize elements, find and replace text, and customize every detail of your tour." />
            <FeatureCard Icon="analytics" Title="Engagement Analytics" Description="Track views, step completion, time-on-step, and conversion events for every demo session." />
            <FeatureCard Icon="person_add" Title="Lead Capture" Description="Built-in lead form at the end of every demo. Export to Excel or connect to your CRM." />
            <FeatureCard Icon="tune" Title="Personalization" Description="Use {{company}} tokens to dynamically swap text for each prospect. One demo, infinite personalization." />
            <FeatureCard Icon="translate" Title="Multilingual" Description="Build demos in English and Spanish. Voiceover auto-detects language. Reach global audiences." />
            <FeatureCard Icon="share" Title="Share Anywhere" Description="Share via link, embed on your website, or copy the embed code. WhatsApp and email sharing built in." />
        </div>
    </div>
</section>

<section class="mkt-section-alt">
    <div class="mkt-container">
        <div class="mkt-section-heading reveal">
            <div class="mkt-eyebrow">Self-Serve Path</div>
            <h2>Start free now. Add sales help only when you need it.</h2>
            <p>Everything on the homepage should help a visitor say yes to trying the product themselves. These are the decision points we should reinforce.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="mkt-grid mkt-grid-3 reveal-stagger">
            <div class="mkt-card mkt-decision-card">
                <div class="mkt-decision-step">01</div>
                <h3>Fast path to value</h3>
                <p>Put the strongest self-serve CTA above the fold and keep it primary across the page. Product exploration should be the fallback, not sales contact.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="mkt-card mkt-decision-card">
                <div class="mkt-decision-step">02</div>
                <h3>Show the workflow, not just claim it</h3>
                <p>The public site should visually demonstrate capture, AI generation, and publish results. That reduces skepticism and pushes users into signup faster.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="mkt-card mkt-decision-card">
                <div class="mkt-decision-step">03</div>
                <h3>Delay the sales ask</h3>
                <p>Keep "Book a demo" available, but secondary. The primary audience here wants to try the product before talking to a person.</p>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</section>

<section class="mkt-section">
    <div class="mkt-container">
        <div class="mkt-testimonial-featured reveal">
            <blockquote>"The public site should feel like the product itself: fast to understand, visually confident, and easy to try without friction."</blockquote>
            <div class="mkt-testimonial-attribution" style="justify-content:center">
                <div>
                    <div class="mkt-testimonial-name">Homepage direction</div>
                    <div class="mkt-testimonial-role">Self-serve first, sales second</div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</section>

<section class="mkt-section-alt" style="background:var(--nt-primary-light)">
    <div class="mkt-container">
        <div class="mkt-section-heading reveal">
            <h2>Results That Speak for Themselves</h2>
        </div>
        <div class="mkt-grid mkt-grid-4 reveal-stagger">
            <MetricCard Value="60s" Label="AI-generated first tour draft" />
            <MetricCard Value="24+" Label="Voices available to preview" />
            <MetricCard Value="HTML/CSS" Label="Capture with visual fidelity" />
            <MetricCard Value="Free" Label="Signup path with no credit card" />
        </div>
    </div>
</section>

